heading: Grinning Labyrinth Dungeon Guide
content: Grinning Labyrinth is a dangerous dungeon with Fallen everywhere, ready to explode and revive their friends. The rare trap on the ground can also you, allowing you to take enormous damage. Druids however, will want to stop by for the . Save this dungeon for when you're well equipped While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
